law.history: Repealed 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 284,sec. 65. -- Amended 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 187, sec. 2 -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 342, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1986. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 384, sec. 490, effective June 17, 1978 -- Created 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 97, sec. 2, effective June 18, 1970.

metadata.lrc-note: This section was amended by the 1988 General Assembly and also repealed. Pursuant to KRS 446.260, the repeal prevails.
